*Example fragment:* "Top Lists Partner Factory — ACTIVE Phase 1+; explicit standalone
direction; ~40% founder attention. Quick-Money AI Consulting — ACTIVE Phase 1; revenue
generator; ~50% founder attention. Brand + Research + Life-OS — operational
maintenance; ~10% combined."

## §5 Hybrid framework binding

Per inferred memory `project_jetix_hybrid_framework_vision`, Jetix is hybrid:
